description:
Idly Dosa Batter: The ID Fresho idli/dosa batter is a ready-made mix that saves your time and energy to create a dosa batter from scratch. Idli and dosa are the most popular healthy south Indian foods. They are made from rice and black lentils. Idlis are made in a specialized mould and eaten with different items like chutney, vegetable stew or other flavorful toppings for breakfast or as a snack. Typically, an idli/dosa batter involves a three-step recipe which includes soaking the rice, grinding and fermenting it. But with this readymade batter, you can make crispy dosa and fluffy soft idlis at no time at all. This Batter serves to cook 17 to 20 idlis of 12 to 14 dosa. Idlis contain no cholesterol, no fat, and no saturated fat. These small healthy south Indian food treats are good for you and, as a bonus, convenient for those on the go. To make your diet a bit healthier, swap a doughnut or muffin for healthy south Indian food idli/dosa.
Whole Wheat Parota: Parota is a subcontinental layered flatbread made from maida or atta, alternatively known as flaky ribbon pancake. If you are looking for something fancy to eat but feeling too lazy to actually make it, ID Fresho Whole Wheat Parota is the perfect thing to buy. A great substitute for homemade Rotis, these paranthas are made of 100% whole wheat and can be eaten any time with your favourite vegetable curry. ID Fresho Whole Wheat parotas are made from wheat flour which is high in fibre and nutrients. These are easy to digest. Refined flour leads to constipation, piles and colon cancer. Hence, whole wheat flour is a healthier substitute.

Blue Bird’s Custard Powder with Pineapple Flavoring has a refreshing and smooth taste that lingers on your taste buds once you have it. Just add some milk and a few stewed or fresh fruits and your desert is ready in just 5 minutes. 

The product is 100% vegetarian and has no cholesterol. It is enriched with Calcium and Vitamins A &C, so it improves your overall body health. You can experiment with it in the form of a fruit salad or custard pudding. 

Directions for Use:

Step 1 -Measure BLUE BIRD custard powder (20 gms for custard sauce, 30 gms for fruit salad, 40 gms for pudding) into a bowl. Add ¼ to ½ cup of milk to make a smooth paste.

Step 2 - Boil 500 ml of milk with 50 gms of sugar stirring it properly. Then, remove it from the heat.

Step 3 - Add the paste and cook again for 2-3 minutes, stirring continuously to avoid burning.

Moulded Pudding – After removing the mixture from the heat, add one teaspoon of butter. Finally, pour it into a wetted mould and leave to set.

Fruit salad – At the final cooking stage, add cream or malai for the best results.

product: Classic Peanut Butter - Crunch, Gluten Free, Non-GMO, Vegan
description:
Alpino was born, when we realized that people in India were lacking a lot of nutrition in their diet, lately resulting number of people suffering from malnutrition in our country. We noticed that most people consumed food that was either, full of sugar or high in empty calories (low nutrition), taking these things in mind we started a campaign to improve India's nutrition by engaging in the health food business. The market was filled with a lot of peanut-butter brands, but it was very difficult to find “pure peanut butter’’, which had absolutely no stabilisers and which literally tasted like a jar of roasted peanuts. Coming to Alpino, we stand miles away from any sort of compromise, be it quality, quantity or taste of any of our products and promise to stay 100% true to our ingredients. Our peanuts are not just normal peanuts, they are unique, they are freshly roasted Alpino peanuts!
We put food safety first, there is nothing more important to us than the quality of our products. Our mission is to nourish people’s lives by offering a wide variety of convenient, delicious, and affordable food choices that can help everyone enjoy a balanced, healthful diet. Furthermore, our peanut butter is produced with the finest raw materials, so that, the moment you take your first bite, you’ll not just like us, you’ll trust us and you’ll believe in us. As a startup, we just do one thing. We put ourself in the customer’s shoe, and which has enabled us to evolve our product our humble beginnings to (one of) the best peanut butter brands in India.
A taste so heavenly, a spread so pure, your kids are going to love it and you too for sure! Alpino peanut butter is the perfect snack for a healthier lifestyle. It is 100% cholesterol-free and contains absolutely no trans fat. It is a great source of protein and is 100% pure. Coming to facts and figures, our peanut butter stays in the jar for only 0.000001 sec before you relish every bit of this unbelievably delicious peanut spread. Amazing right ?! Believe us, who can’t resist a jar of peanut butter so pure. We use no stabilisers and just in case you find a layer of oil floating on top of your jar after a few days, you need not worry, coz that’s a sign of how pure our peanut butter actually is. Alpino peanut butter is the ultimate energy booster and your heart’s best companion, so much so that the next time you take your family to the supermarket, this is the first thing that’s going to go in your basket. Available in 5 amazing variants - peanut butter crunch, peanut butter chocolate, peanut butter smooth, peanut butter natural, powdered peanut butter.

product: Natural Peanut Butter - Smooth, Unsweetened, Gluten Free, Non-GMO, Vegan
description:
Alpino was born, when we realized that people in India were lacking a lot of nutrition in their diet, lately resulting number of people suffering from malnutrition in our country. We noticed that most people consumed food that was either, full of sugar or high in empty calories (low nutrition), taking these things in mind we started a campaign to improve India's nutrition by engaging in the health food business. The market was filled with a lot of peanut-butter brands, but it was very difficult to find “pure peanut butter’’, which had absolutely no stabilisers and which literally tasted like a jar of roasted peanuts. Coming to Alpino, we stand miles away from any sort of compromise, be it quality, quantity or taste of any of our products and promise to stay 100% true to our ingredients. Our peanuts are not just normal peanuts, they are unique, they are freshly roasted Alpino peanuts!
We put food safety first, there is nothing more important to us than the quality of our products. Our mission is to nourish people’s lives by offering a wide variety of convenient, delicious, and affordable food choices that can help everyone enjoy a balanced, healthful diet. Furthermore, our peanut butter is produced with the finest raw materials, so that, the moment you take your first bite, you’ll not just like us, you’ll trust us and you’ll believe in us. As a startup, we just do one thing. We put ourself in the customer’s shoe, and which has enabled us to evolve our product our humble beginnings to (one of) the best peanut butter brands in India.
A taste so heavenly, a spread so pure, your kids are going to love it and you too for sure! Alpino peanut butter is the perfect snack for a healthier lifestyle. It is 100% cholesterol-free and contains absolutely no trans fat. It is a great source of protein and is 100% pure. Coming to facts and figures, our peanut butter stays in the jar for only 0.000001 sec before you relish every bit of this unbelievably delicious peanut spread. Amazing right ?! Believe us, who can’t resist a jar of peanut butter so pure. We use no stabilisers and just in case you find a layer of oil floating on top of your jar after a few days, you need not worry, coz that’s a sign of how pure our peanut butter actually is. Alpino peanut butter is the ultimate energy booster and your heart’s best companion, so much so that the next time you take your family to the supermarket, this is the first thing that’s going to go in your basket. Available in 5 amazing variants - peanut butter crunch, peanut butter chocolate, peanut butter smooth, peanut butter natural, powdered peanut butter.

Peas are delivered fresh to the factory. Each load is sampled and assessed for the grade, foreign material and physical defects. The product is blanched to give a trace positive peroxidase reaction between 60 and 90 seconds. Frozen peas palletainers are then labelled and transferred to the cold store where they are stored at minus 23-degree centigrade until required for packing.During packing the peas are inspected before weighing and filling into poly-lined cartons. The uniform size of peas would be 9 to 11 mm in diameter. The peas are double sorted and graded to ensure that the uniformity of size is maintained.The cartons are best before and production date coded, check weighed and metal detected, palletised and stretch wrapped before being returned to store at minus 23-degree centigrade to await dispatch. Directions for Use:

Step 1 -Measure BLUE BIRD custard powder (20 gms for custard sauce, 30 gms for fruit salad, 40 gms for pudding) into a bowl. Add ¼ to ½ cup of milk to make a smooth paste.

Step 2 - Boil 500 ml of milk with 50 gms of sugar stirring it properly. Then, remove it from the heat.

Step 3 - Add the paste and cook again for 2-3 minutes, stirring continuously to avoid burning.

Moulded Pudding – After removing the mixture from the heat, add one teaspoon of butter. Finally, pour it into a wetted mould and leave to set.

Fruit salad – At the final cooking stage, add cream or malai for the best results.
